@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.30)) * wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.51)))
    v2 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.08) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.37)) + 0.55)
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp))
    tmp = ((v2 / tmp) + ((v1 + 0.70 * tmp + 0.46) + wp.abs(v0 + 0.93)))
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.57) * (v1 + 0.12 - v2 + 0.57)) + wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.36)))
    v2 = v2
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.33)) / ((v1 + 0.15 + tmp + 0.70) * tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
